<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 21:14:24 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国在伦敦新建大型大使馆的计划遭到当地官员拒绝</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-plans-large-new-london-embassy-rejected-by-local-officials-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国在伦敦设立新大型大使馆的计划周一被当地官员拒绝，理由是这可能对附近居民构成安全风险，这给中央政府带来了拒绝该规划申请的压力。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 21:08:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-plans-large-new-london-embassy-rejected-by-local-officials-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>国会可能禁止两家中国制造商生产新无人机</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/dji-could-be-banned-launching-new-products-us-under-proposed-bill-2024-12-09/</link><description>根据美国众议院将于本周晚些时候投票的年度军事法案，中国大疆创新和 Autel Robotics 可能被禁止在美国市场销售新无人机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 19:21:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/dji-could-be-banned-launching-new-products-us-under-proposed-bill-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>币安首席执行官滕表示，币安仍在选择全球总部地点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-still-choose-location-global-headquarters-ceo-teng-says-2024-12-09/</link><description>加密货币交易所币安网首席执行官周一对路透表示，该公司尚未决定其全球总部的设立地点，此前该公司曾表示即将做出决定，但该高管指出了该公司为改善公司治理而采取的举措。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 18:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/binance-still-choose-location-global-headquarters-ceo-teng-says-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>法国欧安诺将与中国XTC成立两家合资企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/frances-orano-set-up-two-jvs-with-chinas-xtc-2024-12-09/</link><description>法国核电集团欧安诺周一宣布与中国XTC新能源材料集团成立两家合资企业，在法国敦刻尔克生产电动汽车电池组件。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 17:53:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/frances-orano-set-up-two-jvs-with-chinas-xtc-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪在欧洲扩张中将重点关注插电式混合动力汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-focus-plug-in-hybrid-cars-european-expansion-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪在欧洲的特别顾问周一表示，由于全电动汽车需求疲软，混合动力技术将成为该公司在欧洲扩张的关键。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 15:54:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-focus-plug-in-hybrid-cars-european-expansion-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>在欧盟的中国企业表示，在全球紧张局势中，商业环境更加严峻</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</link><description>周一公布的一项调查显示，在欧盟的中国企业表示，商业环境连续第五年恶化，地缘政治紧张局势加剧和反华情绪阻碍了运营。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/business-conditions-tougher-chinese-firms-eu-say-amid-global-tensions-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>字节跳动、TikTok 寻求暂时停止美国禁令，等待最高法院审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国字节跳动及其短视频应用 TikTok 周一请求上诉法院暂时阻止一项法律，该法律要求母公司字节跳动在 1 月 19 日之前剥离 TikTok，否则将面临禁令，等待美国最高法院的审查。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 14:21:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/legal/bytedance-tiktok-seek-temporary-halt-us-crackdown-law-pending-supreme-court-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>随着需求不断增长，中国小米将于明年夏天推出新款 SUV</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-announces-new-suv-launch-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国电子产品制造商小米周一表示，预计将在明年 6 月或 7 月推出首款 SUV YU7，进一步进军中国竞争激烈的汽车市场。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:20:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-xiaomi-announces-new-suv-launch-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>LGIM表示对中国不太乐观；英国后备母猪报价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-lgim-urgent-2024-12-09/</link><description>Legal &amp;amp; General Investment Management 首席投资官索尼娅·劳德 (Sonja Laud) 周一表示，中国仍面临非常困难的经济形势，目前还很难对世界第二大经济体持乐观态度。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 12:19:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-lgim-urgent-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国针对英伟达展开反垄断调查，加剧美国芯片紧张局势</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-investigates-nvidia-over-suspected-violation-antimonopoly-law-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国周一表示，已对英伟达公司(Nvidia Corp)涉嫌违反中国反垄断法的行为展开调查，此举被广泛视为对华盛顿对中国芯片行业最新限制的报复。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/china-investigates-nvidia-over-suspected-violation-antimonopoly-law-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>美洲 美联储降息，中国改变货币立场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-09/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 11:10:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国货币宽松立场推动矿业股和能源股提振富时 100 指数</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/miners-propel-uks-ftse-100-higher-gdp-data-tap-2024-12-09/</link><description>英国富时 100 指数周一在能源和矿业股的推动下攀升，投资者关注本周的国内 GDP 数据来衡量英国央行的政策前景。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 10:27:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/miners-propel-uks-ftse-100-higher-gdp-data-tap-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>前俄罗斯 ASML 员工被指控盗窃知识产权和违反制裁行为</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-russian-asml-employee-set-court-hearing-alleged-ip-theft-case-2024-12-09/</link><description>荷兰一家法院周一延长了对半导体设备制造商 ASML 一名俄罗斯前雇员的拘留，该雇员涉嫌窃取知识产权并将其出售给俄罗斯买家，违反了欧洲制裁。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:59:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/former-russian-asml-employee-set-court-hearing-alleged-ip-theft-case-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>受中国刺激预期影响，欧洲股市收于六周高点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-bounce-china-stimulus-optimism-2024-12-09/</link><description>在承诺推出新的刺激措施以支持中国放缓的经济之后，欧洲股市周一收于六周以来的最高水平，其中矿业和奢侈品股领涨。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:32:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/european-shares-bounce-china-stimulus-optimism-2024-12-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国誓言加大政策刺激力度，刺激2025年经济增长</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-first-monetary-policy-shift-since-2010-spur-growth-2024-12-09/</link><description>中国将采取“适度宽松”的货币政策，这是近14年来首次放松政策。</description><pubDate>Mon, 09 Dec 2024 08:29:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-announces-first-monetary-policy-shift-since-2010-spur-growth-2024-12-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>